A RESOLUTION
1 Commending the Milton Lady Eagles lacrosse team for winning the 2024 GHSA 7A Girls
2 Lacrosse State Championship; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the Milton Lady Eagles lacrosse team has established and maintained a proud
4 tradition of excellence with equal emphases on character and academics; and
5 WHEREAS, this superlative team has completed another triumphant season of lacrosse
6 competition by posting an excellent record of 18 wins and only four losses; and
7 WHEREAS, excellent play, superior teamwork, and extraordinary resilience made this team
8 a spectacular one to observe throughout the season, and as a fitting finale to its remarkable
9 2024 campaign, the team captured its 17th girls lacrosse state championship in school history
10 and fourth state championship in a row; and
11 WHEREAS, the phenomenal performance of the team is a clear indication of the outstanding
12 athletic ability, the dedication and hard work, and the unity of purpose and spirit of each
13 member of the team; its superb offensive and defensive talents; and the astute direction of
14 Head Coach Tim Godby; and
